turtl3.data

Class DataController

  • java.lang.Object
    • turtl3.data.DataController

  • public class DataController
extends java.lang.Object
    Controls the programmed data elements. This includes adding and removing commands or running the program. The class further writes programs to and loads programs from the file-system.
    Author:
    PKissmer

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description

      Generates a new DataController with an empty data list.
